you two feel good about it?

01:38.432 --> 01:40.248
Sure, yeah.
But do we have to do this?

01:40.267 --> 01:41.842
Sorry, it's
unexpected pairings

01:41.936 --> 01:43.160
so we don't tip the season.

01:43.162 --> 01:44.511
Yeah, fine.

01:44.663 --> 01:46.271
Maybe we could do
a popular dance or something.

01:46.423 --> 01:48.273
How about the electric slide?

01:48.425 --> 01:50.142
Oh, am I
at a banquet hall wedding?

01:50.294 --> 01:51.426
Okay, that's a no.

01:51.595 --> 01:52.778
What's your favorite
dance movie?

01:52.929 --> 01:53.946
I don't know.

01:54.173 --> 01:55.447
My mom says the movie theaters
are for people

01:55.599 --> 01:57.174
