air-conditioning.

01:57.267 --> 01:59.767
I'm gonna kill you.

01:59.845 --> 02:00.953
Just gotta get through this.

02:01.180 --> 02:02.529
Did you play video games?

02:02.681 --> 02:04.865
Every day after school,
Justin and I would play<i> RRD.</i>

02:04.959 --> 02:07.684
Shut up.
Yes, I was obsessed.

02:07.777 --> 02:09.611
Simon and I used to play
<i> Rhythm Rhythm Dancer</i>

02:09.630 --> 02:12.189
all the time
when we lived on a cruise ship.

02:12.207 --> 02:13.373
Sorry, what?
You lived on a cruise ship?

02:13.525 --> 02:15.300
We were
onboard entertainment.

02:15.452 --> 02:19.029
That is so interesting, and it
explains so much about you.

02:19.047 --> 02:21.789
Should we, like,
do an<i> RRD</i> dance?

02:21.884 --> 02:23.124
Hell yeah.
Let's do it.

02:23.218 --> 02:24.384
Yeah, we can make that happen.

02:24.478 --> 02:29.055
