their tears, but wait,

05:39.748 --> 05:41.231
it's the after show.

05:41.249 --> 05:42.341
Monica and Wayne
are introducing America

05:42.492 --> 05:44.659
to our cast,
and here is something

05:44.753 --> 05:45.919
you're gonna love.

05:46.071 --> 05:47.737
<i> ("Ain't No Mountain</i>
<i> High Enough" playing)</i>

05:47.756 --> 05:49.664
Uh-huh?

