<i> I mean, I just feel like</i>

06:31.875 --> 06:36.636
<i> it would go a long way</i>
<i> to forgiving past mistakes.</i>

06:36.788 --> 06:38.622
<i> You know,</i>
<i> if this show were a big hit,</i>

06:38.640 --> 06:40.974
<i> I just think it would be</i>
<i> received warmly.</i>

