<i> could make people</i>

06:44.646 --> 06:46.571
<i> maybe forget about some stuff</i>
<i> that happened</i>

06:46.648 --> 06:48.073
<i> in a house that was</i>
<i> out in the ocean.</i>

06:48.300 --> 06:49.557
<i> Feel free to say no.</i>
<i> Say no if you wanna say no.</i>

06:49.651 --> 06:51.576
<i> If you wanna say no,</i>
<i> just say no to me right now,</i>

06:51.728 --> 06:54.821
<i> but I just--it would be</i>
<i> really great</i>

06:54.915 --> 06:57.332
<i> if this was received warmly.</i>

06:58.644 --> 07:00.401
