-Copy that.

07:24.278 --> 07:25.444
First things first--Dante?

07:25.595 --> 07:27.504
I just walked
in a circle, didn't I?

07:27.522 --> 07:30.173
-You did, boss.
-Okay, all right, guys!

07:30.192 --> 07:31.783
Hey, ain't no mountain high,

07:31.935 --> 07:33.343
ain't no valley low

07:33.345 --> 07:35.537
to keep us from making
a live show.

